# Parallel Builds
##  Jenkins Pipeline â€” Parallel Build & Test
You will learn how to **run build and test in parallel**.

pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Parallel Tasks') {
            parallel {
                stage('Build') {
                    steps {
                        sh 'mvn clean compile'
                    }
                }
                stage('Test') {
                    steps {
                        sh 'mvn test'
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
### Jenkins creates separate executors
Build and Test run simultaneously
If any parallel stage fails, the pipeline fails

## ðŸ”¹ GitLab CI â€” Parallel Jobs
You will learn how to **run parallel jobs in GitLab CI**.

stages:
  - build-test

maven-build:
  stage: build-test
  image: maven:3.8.1-jdk-17
  script:
    - git clone https://github.com/Pathnex/sample-java-app.git
    - cd sample-java-app
    - mvn clean compile
  parallel: 1

maven-test:
  stage: build-test
  image: maven:3.8.1-jdk-17
  script:
    - cd sample-java-app
    - mvn test

### (Run in parallel
    Have access to the repo
    Use the same base image)
  parallel: 1
